210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a113fe08a178aec9697f5131c6360cafca43b2c4","tid":1182992,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T14:55:38.000Z","msg":"大排量NA3.0以上直6,V6<br />\n去到盡都係300p多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n油價仲要講緊$1.8公里以上<br />\nV8 個d去到4000cc Up都係400p多d<br />\n但肯定做緊$2.5公里以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家個d新興引擎2.0T性能小小既話<br />\n出廠都250p以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />油錢更加做到$1.5公里內<br />\n改下進排寫份stage更加可以300p以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底NA車仲有冇佢既價值？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我本人係好鐘意大排量NA車既低扭。聲音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n奈何時代真係進步緊。<br />\n連turbo都撐唔住慢慢變成電車<br />\n我真係唔敢想像十年後睇賽車係完全冇引擎炮烤聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我相信過多十年，澳門格蘭披治會剩低高頻摩打聲<br />\n將來真係唔撚想揸電車啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:36:52.000Z","msg":"小弟窮L 係云云咁多架NA 入面最大都係玩過 V8 NA 4000cc 反應係真係一流,<br />\n尤其係扯高D轉數時架車嘅反應真心正到不行了<br />\n係D 油好似倒水咁, around $2.5/km"},{"pid":"f6924600d81121be23e5267077f49a8368c61957","tid":1182992,"uid":91638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a9c61f430ff8919e0544fa14ded3ec4dbfedbb6","tid":1182992,"uid":72085,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ecd0a7b28160c3cd50e286a44be49b783c1beb85","tid":1182992,"uid":29497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:59:48.000Z","msg":"得mazda仲好集中搞汽油引擎+NA車<br />\nBut...."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:56:07.000Z","msg":"佢係落足心機搞慳油NA車，但一間廠扭轉唔到大局，始終數據差過turbo車，好難賣，同埋香港渣車低扭好緊要，要轉線爬頭出路口都講個快字，D人又唔肯讓，唯有渣架夠爆既車<br />\n我諗遲下連turbo 都收皮，用48v電做過渡，最終都係要全電動，趁有得玩好玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:46:09.000Z","msg":"反而想知佢